XBMC NextPVR Add-on
----------------------------------------------
Written by: Graeme Blackley
HomePage:   http://www.nextpvr.com
Contact:    http://www.nextpvr.com/contact/

----------------------------------------------
Supported platforms:
- Windows
- Linux
- OSX (should work, not tested by me)

Dependencies:
- NextPVR 3.1.1 or higher.
 
